{"tid":581763,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"轉灣定轉彎呀? 坤哥字都未寫好教做人道理","createTime":"2018-03-05T15:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T15:30:15.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5311e32fb66f1c7b6f8be799b79d201739e64009","tid":581763,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"近日吳業坤（坤哥）去咗日本渡假，除咗食同買之外，佢仲去埋滑雪添，佢放咗段片上社交網站，睇落都有姿勢有實際嘅，不話佢個標題就成為熱話，皆因佢話：「做人同滑雪一樣要學識轉灣。」，無錯，就係個「灣」字出問題喇，網民留言話佢「轉灣」定「轉彎」都唔識，應該要學寫字先，再加上條片只係影佢直衝，網民就回應：「幾好喎！後生仔係要衝下」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180305/large/1520251292_c4bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520251292_c4bc.png&h=f2fc5820&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59e42df02d71ec61071e57208f4296dbff0cace1","tid":581763,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16a00095a5287f525d89863128b76d56917356d5","tid":581763,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59e42df02d71ec61071e57208f4296dbff0cace1","tid":581763,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:30:15.000Z","msg":"去佢fb留言會唔會實際啲?"}]}